Bai Ze, I...

4
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:22,120
Immortal Bai Ze.

5
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:28,320
Bai Ze, I don't like her.

6
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:30,040
Besides, we don't even know who she is.

7
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:31,320
If you bring her back
without much thought,

8
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:33,160
my father won't allow it.

9
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,520
Master has a benevolent heart.

10
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:41,040
He took care of an orphan like me
since I was a child.

11
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:43,560
How could he not welcome
a vulnerable girl?

12
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,960
I'll bring her back first.

13
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:48,360
I'll be responsible if anything happens.

14
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,000
Bai Ze,

15
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,680
is this Qingyun Sect?

16
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:22,720
Yes, take this place
as your own home from now on.

17
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:50,600
I wonder if Bai Ze likes flower baths.

18
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,720
I don't want you
to treat me like a sister.

19
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,600
If you're grateful to my father
for raising you,

20
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,720
you should marry me,

21
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,600
love me, dote on me,
and take care of me for life.

22
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,920
I've told you so many times.

23
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,240
I only see you as a sibling.

24
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,520
I have no romantic feelings
toward you at all.

25
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,880
What about Qinghuan?

26
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,560
What does this have to do with Qinghuan?

27
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:12,160
Mount Qingyun is my territory.

28
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,640
If she keeps harassing you,

29
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,760
I'll drive her down the mountain.

30
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,040
I'm in trouble.

31
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,360
I'm going to take my bath.

32
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,240
So please stop following me.

33
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,040
What's wrong with Martial Brother?

34
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,800
Who's there?

35
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:12,800
You wretch.

36
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:19,960
Why are you here?

37
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:23,400
I wanted to prepare
a flower bath for you.

38
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:27,160
But I overheard Miss Linyue wants
to drive me down the mountain.

39
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,440
So I... I tried to...

40
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:34,760
Don't worry.

41
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,520
Linyue may appear arrogant and willful.

42
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,240
But she's kind and honest.

43
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,520
She won't drive you away.

44
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,600
(That shameless woman
has bewitched Eldest Martial Brother.)

45
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,000
(If I barged in now,)

46
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,600
(he would never take my side.)

47
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,940
(Heavenly Dungeon)

48
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,080
Bai Ze, I want to go with you.

49
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,320
Why are you following me again?

50
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,320
I've told you so many times

51
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,800
Heavenly Dungeon is a forbidden area.
No one can enter freely.

52
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,440
You should go back now.

53
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,240
No.

54
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,360
That old fogey of the Demonic Sect
is very tight-lipped.

55
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,760
If we interrogate him together,

56
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,560
we may find out the whereabouts
of the Secret Art of Youming.

57
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,720
Who's there?

58
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,640
Why are you here?

59
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:40,000
Well, you trespassed
the forbidden area of Qingyun Sect.

60
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,720
I've finally caught you red-handed.

61
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,200
We should get it straight
before accusing her.

62
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,200
Forbidden area?

63
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:47,600
I didn't know this was a forbidden area.

64
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,000
Bai Ze,

65
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,800
I only want to follow you.

66
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,640
It was my fault for not telling you.

67
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,600
Why don't you go back first?

68
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,400
It's dangerous here.

69
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,240
She can't leave.

70
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,640
She trespassed into the forbidden area
without any reason.

71
00:04:58,640 --> 00:05:00,440
