will be kicked out of the sect.

72
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,360
We ought to punish
an outsider like her severely.

73
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:06,160
Bai Ze, I'll tell Father about this

74
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,360
if you let her go today.

75
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,320
Those who don't know are not at fault.

76
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,840
I brought her back here.

77
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,600
So I'll be responsible
if anything happens.

78
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,520
We have trouble, Eldest Martial Brother!

79
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:20,480
The Nangong Family
came here with rage looking for you,

80
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,760
saying they want
to settle scores with you.

81
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,840
Master.

82
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,240
Bai Ze of the Qingyun Sect!

83
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,960
A lad like you sure is arrogant.

84
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:45,080
Did you pick on the Nangong Family,
thinking we're weak?

85
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,440
Elder He,

86
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:53,440
Nangong Jun didn't hesitate
to kill innocent young women

87
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,640
to sacrifice them as the bride
for Ghost Bridegroom.

88
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,640
As a disciple of the Qingyun Sect,

89
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,920
