92
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,640
That's what you said.

93
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:10,040
Jun would never collude
with Ghost Bridegroom.

94
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,440
To offer the women as ghost brides,

95
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:14,560
