to control the villagers.

96
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,440
Evil energy would enter anyone's lungs

97
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,520
who shakes the Soul-Calling Bell.

98
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,440
It'll also remain within the chest.

99
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,240
If we want to confirm this matter,

100
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:23,440
