108
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:48,880
Master, I would never do anything
against my conscience.

109
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,280
I don't regret my action.

110
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:52,640
But it's my fault
for implicating Qingyun Sect.

111
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,080
I'm willing to accept any punishment.

112
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,160
Bai Ze, the eldest disciple
of the Qingyun Sect,

113
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,760
